sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Gateway
    participant EnvelopeValidator
    participant Auth as Identity/Attestation
    participant Service as Decision Service
    participant GSM as Governance SM
    participant Repo as Repository

    Client->>Gateway: POST /envelopes/submit
    Gateway->>EnvelopeValidator: validate schema + integrity

    EnvelopeValidator->>Auth: verify identity + authority
    Auth-->>EnvelopeValidator: OK

    EnvelopeValidator->>Service: route(protocol)

    Service->>GSM: apply transition
    GSM-->>Service: new state

    Service->>Repo: persist decision + history
    Repo-->>Service: OK

    Service-->>Gateway: response
    Gateway-->>Client: 200 OK
